des: Dry Cleaning and Laundry becomes easier with pickup and delivery dry cleaning and laundry services. Just say 'Alexa, open my dry cleaner' to get started! Now you can tell my dry cleaner you are on your way so they can have your clothes ready by the time you get there! Just say, 'Alexa, tell my dry cleaner I am on my way' to let my dry cleaner know you are on your way!
